settings.description: Climb through the grassy and rope-heavy Green Climb Skies, where you encounter various enemies along the way. Re-Issue of "Green Climb Contest", prod. Code = #111B, Rel. Date: 9/19/22, 5:02pm
This course includes the new SMB2 mushroom!
Una aventura de mario en los mundos secretos, viajara al bosque, y el mundo de agua, el mundo de las cataratas, y por ultimo castillo de larry koopa
